Comment: Once again, a never-say-die attitude pays dividends :-)  My last game in the 2009 Championship.  When we started this game jklarl's rating was way higher than mine, so I started with the strategic 1. d4, as I feel that slower styled games give me a better chance against better players.  Crash bang wallop open games tend to end up with me being the walloped one.
